<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Welcome to Beauty Bliss</title>
    <style type="text/css">
      body {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        height: 100vh;
        min-width: 100%;
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 1.5;
        color: #222222;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #a800ff, #ff00c8);
      }

      a {
        color: #fff;
        text-decoration: none;
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: 24px;
        font-weight: 700;
        line-height: 1.25;
        margin-top: 0;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .status {
        color: #fff;
        width: 100px;
        padding: 10px;
        animation: blink 2s infinite;
        text-align: center;
        margin: 0 auto;
      }

      @keyframes blink {
        from {
          opacity: 0;
        }

        to {
          opacity: 1;
        }
      }

      p {
        margin-top: 0;
        margin-bottom: 24px;
      }

      .divider {
        border-top: 1px solid #ccc;
        margin: 20px 0;
      }

      .email-wrapper {
        max-width: 700px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background-color: #fff;
        padding: 20px;
      }

      .email-header {
        background-color: #1e1e1e;
        padding: 30px;
        color: #f086d9;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .email-body {
        padding: 14px;
        background-color: #f4f3f3;
        height: 70vh;
      }

      .email-footer {
        background-color: #1e1e1e;
        padding: 14px;
        color: #d55fbb;
        text-align: center;
      }

      img {
        padding: 24px;
        max-width: 100%;
        height: auto;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="email-wrapper">
      <div class="email-header">
        <img
          src="cid:logo"
          height="120"
          width="120"
          alt="D' Plush Choice Logo"
          style="
            display: block;
            margin: 0 auto;
            border-radius: 50%;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(168, 0, 255, 0.15);
            background: #fff;
          "
        />
        <h1 style="color: #a800ff; margin-top: 10px">
          Welcome to D' Plush Choice!
        </h1>
      </div>
      <div
        class="email-body"
        style="
          border-radius: 16px;
          box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(255, 0, 200, 0.08);
          margin-top: -30px;
        "
      >
        <p style="font-size: 18px; color: #a800ff; font-weight: 600">
          Hello <%= name %>,
        </p>
        <p style="color: #222; font-size: 16px">
          We are
          <span style="color: #ff00c8; font-weight: 600">thrilled</span> to
          welcome you to <b>D' Plush Choice</b>, your new go-to destination for
          all things beauty. We're here to help you discover products that match
          your style and elevate your beauty routine.
        </p>
        <p style="color: #222; font-size: 16px">
          Stay tuned for
          <span style="color: #a800ff; font-weight: 600">exclusive offers</span
          >, beauty tips, and the latest trends directly in your inbox.
        </p>
        <p style="color: #222; font-size: 16px">
          If you have any questions or need assistance, feel free to
          <a
            href="mailto:support@dplushchoice.com"
            style="color: #ff00c8; text-decoration: underline"
            >contact us</a
          >.
        </p>
        <p style="font-size: 17px; color: #a800ff; font-weight: 600">
          Thank you for joining us. Let's make beauty blissful!
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="email-footer">
        <p>&copy;2025 D' Plush Choice. All rights reserved.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
